      "content": "idk i just dont want to end up in the er if i dont have to. it happens to me sometimes where my face feels heavy during a migraine. u think there is a chance it's just a hemiplegic migraine or something? i have some sumatriptan in my cabinet, should i just take a couple of those and try to sleep it off?",
